INSERT INTO `wp_postmeta` VALUES("1382", "151", "wpcf-action-description-in-english", "The action promotes the development of networks of competence centers in thematic areas that will be defined through the process of entrepreneurial discovery. It concerns networks of laboratories and national-scale infrastructures that will support the needs of enterprises, public services, public utilities, local government, etc. These laboratories may belong to universities, research centers or more generally in the public sector and provide scientific and technical services. These networks are expected to enhance their sustainability also from innovation vouchers. \r\n\r\nΤhe main objective of this action is to support the technological needs of the productive resources in areas with significant potential for the restructuring of the Greek economy. In other words, it aims to strengthen laboratory infrastructures for the development of long-term collaborations and filling gaps and weaknesses identified during the process of entrepreneurial discovery.");
