INSERT INTO `wp_postmeta` VALUES("1490", "184", "wpcf-action-plan-title-in-english", "Research and Innovation Strategy for Smart Specialisation");
INSERT INTO `wp_postmeta` VALUES("1491", "184", "wpcf-action-plan-description-in-english", "Within the Europe Strategy 2020 Intelligent Specialisation (RIS3, research and innovation smart specialisation strategy) is defined agendas of economic change that should support the regions by investing in priorities and development needs based on knowledge. The Generalitat de Catalunya presented the working document for the strategy for intelligent specialisation in Catalonia RIS3CAT in July 2013. The document covers the European and Catalan contexts and gives an accurate analysis of the present Catalan economy with its strengths and weaknesses and it establishes the proposal for intelligent specialisation in Catalonia, ECAT 2020, for 2014-2020, specifying a series of instruments to make it possible. The document forms the route map of the current Catalan government and articulates the strategies that will lead to a reactivation of the economy and a reorientation of the production sector towards a more intelligent economic model based on knowledge and innovation. The model is more sustainable with better use of resources and more integrating, creating jobs and strengthening social and regional cohesion.");
