INSERT INTO `wp_postmeta` VALUES("941", "185", "wpcf-action-description-in-english", "This action promotes the development of new emerging activities in Catalonia, based on disruptive technologies and innovative processes and aiming to open new markets or transform existing ones. It focuses on new technologies and technological applications have the following characteristics:\r\n1. The European Union is clearly committed as a strategy for the future and are a priority in Horizon 2020 program.\r\n2. They have a high potential to generate new economic activities.\r\n3. The priority in the context of research and innovation policies of the Government of Catalonia.\r\nThe central element of the project was the creation or extension of demonstration platforms for new technologies addressed to the productive sector. Other activities that can be funded are: \r\n- Assessment of new knowledge and new technologies to be transferred to the market.\r\n- Projects of public-private partnerships to accelerate market introduction of new products or processes.\r\n- Mobility of scientific and technological personnel between universities, scientific institutions, research centers and companies.\r\n- Promote and support the creation of new technology-based companies.\r\n- Specific training programs.");
