6/collaboration.jpg\" width=\"425\" height=\"268\" class=\"img-responsive center-block img-rounded\" />\n<dl>\n  <dt><a href=\"http://actionplan.s3platform.eu/co-design-your-regions-action-plan/\">Co-design Your Region’s Action Plan</a></dt>\n<dd>Search and browse action plans based on their Region and Consultation Status (Open / Closed).</dd>\n</dl>\n<dl>\n  <dt><a href=\"http://actionplan.s3platform.eu/find-a-relevant-action/\">Find a Relevant Action</a></dt>\n<dd>Search and browse actions based on their Thematic Objectives / Investment Priorities, Target groups / Beneficiaries and Involved Actors.</dd>\n</dl>\n</div>\n</div></div></div></div>", "Create or Participate to an Action Plan Co-design Process", "", "inherit", "closed", "closed", "", "107-revision-v1", "", "", "2017-09-06 15:32:00", "2017-09-06 12:32:00", "", "107", "http://actionplan.s3platform.eu/2017/09/06/107-revision-v1/", "0", "revision", "", "0");
